function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	--spawn the inn NPCs
	Hydra.EventSend("QST_Kehj_Caldeum_Inn_Spawn")
	
	--play the effect
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(Marker_Inarius_FX, 10)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(Marker_Inarius_FX, Effect_Inarius_Spotted, true)
	
	--get follower references
	local followerNeyrelle = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(neyrelleFollowerSNO)
	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(lorathFollowerSNO)
	
	-- play the "Inarius" line on the player who entered the trigger
	-- then wait for it to complete
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(Conv_Inarius_Spot_Player, idActor)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(Conv_Inarius_Spot_Player)
	
	-- if this player has followers, let them respond with the followup convo
	if Hydra.ActorGetFollowTarget(followerNeyrelle) == idActor then
	
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(Conv_Inarius_Spotted, idActor, followerNeyrelle, followerLorath)
	end
	
	-- remove blocker & collision for the inn
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(Inn_Blocker)
	Hydra.QActorKill(Inn_Blocker)
	
	for i, idInnCollision in ipairs( Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Caldeum_Inn_Blocker")) do 
		Hydra.ActorDisable(idInnCollision, true)
		end
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(Marker_Inarius_FX, Effect_Inarius_Spotted)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(Conv_Caldeum_Inn, idActor)
	
	
	
end
